Bobby Cole Norris was heartbroken when his mother Kym Norris was diagnosed with leukaemia last August . 
  He launched the #savebobbysmum appeal to urge people to sign up as stem cell donors . 
  Kym had to have a stem cell transplant after being diagnosed with acute myeloid leukemia . 
  Bobby has thanked an anonymous donor who was a match for his mother . 
  He inspired more than 3,000 to sign the bone marrow donation register in one week . 
 